          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "Like normal objects, a painted ram has Hardness. This Hardness reduces any damage it takes by an amount equal to the Hardness. Once a painted ram is reduced to less than half its Hit Points, or immediately upon being damaged by a critical hit, its construct armor breaks, removing the Hardness and reducing its Armor Class to 23.",
